'''Ranged''' is an [[attack type]] that is used primarily by weapons like [[bow]]s, [[Crossbow (weapon)|crossbow]]s and [[thrown weapon]]s. In contrary to most [[melee]] weapons, ranged weapons can be used to deal damage to non-adjacent opponents up to a maximum range of 10 squares depending on the weapon type. Ranged weapons are associated with the [[Ranged]] combat skill.

==Weapons==
===Exclusive===

The following weapon types offer only ranged-based attacks.

